# Form Builder

## PROJECT DESCRIPTION
- Form Builder is a web app that allows you to build forms.
- A form can have multiple pages.
- Pages can be grouped into Groups.
- Pages can have multiple Elements.
- Elements can be inputs, buttons, text fields, etc.
- Every element has a template that defines the type of element and its properties.
- When an element is added to a page, its properties are defined by the template but can be overridden.
- Validation rules can be applied to elements, pages, groups and form.
- Validation rules are based on JSON Logic.

